text: José María "Txiki" Benegas Haddad (25 July 1948 - 25 August 2015) was a Spanish politician. He was a member of the Spanish Socialist Workers' Party (PSOE). He was born in Caracas, Venezuela. Benegas died in Madrid, Spain from cancer at the age of 67.Muere Txiki Benegas, figura clave del socialismo vasco, El Mundo, 25 August 2015 ==References== Category:1948 births Category:2015 deaths Category:People from Caracas Category:Spanish Socialist Workers' Party politicians
